Skindesign for VDR's text2skin-plugin

* for unmodded DVB-Cards 90kB: max. OSD-Height/Width 90% !
* small+simple, no Gfx except symbols
* default vdr-fonts Osd/Sml/Fix


Written by:		Uwe Hanke <egal@egal-vdr.de>

Project's homepage:				www.egal-vdr.de/skins
Latest version available at:	www.egal-vdr.de/skins

